                     Shrew gallery
                     =============

Shrew gallery is an small web gallery using PHP. This gallery is different from
existing gallery because it permit to create a very simple gallery in few
seconds if you have a existing web server :

- upload your photos with FTP in a folder.
- upload 'index.php'
- It work !

The goal is to share easily and quickly your photos without complexe configuration.
If you want 2 albums, create 2 folders, and copy 2 shrew gallery.

The project licence is GNU Affero General Public Licence.

* Official web site: http://shrew-gallery.b219.org/
* Project management page: https://gna.org/projects/shrew-gallery/
